name: Snivy
pokedex: They photosynthesize by bathing their tails in sunlight. When they are not feeling well, their tails droop.

name: Servine
pokedex: They avoid attacks by sinking into the shadows of thick foliage. They retaliate with masterful whipping techniques.

name: Serperior
pokedex: They raise their heads to intimidate opponents, but only give it their all when fighting a powerful opponent.

name: Tepig
pokedex: It blows fire through its nose. When it catches a cold, the fire becomes pitch-black smoke instead.

name: Pignite
pokedex: Whatever it eats becomes fuel for the flame in its stomach. When it is angered, the intensity of the flame increases.

name: Emboar
pokedex: It can throw a fire punch by setting its fists on fire with its fiery chin. It cares deeply about its friends.

name: Oshawott
pokedex: The scalchop on its stomach is made from the same elements as claws. It detaches the scalchop for use as a blade.

name: Dewott
pokedex: Scalchop techniques differ from one Dewott to another. It never neglects maintaining its scalchops.

name: Samurott
pokedex: Part of the armor on its anterior legs becomes a giant sword. Its cry alone is enough to intimidate most enemies.

name: Patrat
pokedex: Extremely cautious, they take shifts to maintain a constant watch of their nest. They feel insecure without a lookout.

name: Watchog
pokedex: They make the patterns on their bodies shine in order to threaten predators. Keen eyesight lets them see in the dark.

name: Lillipup
pokedex: The long hair around its face provides an amazing radar that lets it sense subtle changes in its surroundings.

name: Herdier
pokedex: It loyally follows its Trainer's orders. For ages, they have helped Trainers raise Pokémon.

name: Stoutland
pokedex: This extremely wise Pokémon excels at rescuing people stranded at sea or in the mountains.

name: Purrloin
pokedex: Its cute act is a ruse. When victims let down their guard, they find their items taken. It attacks with sharp claws.

name: Liepard
pokedex: Stealthily, it sneaks up on its target, striking from behind before its victim has a chance to react.

name: Pansage
pokedex: It shares the leaf on its head with weary-looking Pokémon. These leaves are known to relieve stress.

name: Simisage
pokedex: Ill tempered, it fights by swinging its barbed tail around wildly. The leaf growing on its head is very bitter.

name: Pansear
pokedex: This Pokémon lives in caves in volcanoes. The fire within the tuft on its head can reach 600º F.

name: Simisear
pokedex: A flame burns inside its body. It scatters embers from its head and tail to sear its opponents.

name: Panpour
pokedex: It does not thrive in dry environments. It keeps itself damp by shooting water stored in its head tuft from its tail.

name: Simipour
pokedex: The high-pressure water expelled from its tail is so powerful, it can destroy a concrete wall.

name: Munna
pokedex: It eats the dreams of people and Pokémon. When it eats a pleasant dreams, it expels pink-colored mist.

name: Musharna
pokedex: With the mist from its forehead, it can create shapes of things from dreams it has eaten.

name: Pidove
pokedex: These Pokémon live in cities. They are accustomed to people. Flocks often gather in parks and plazas.

name: Tranquill
pokedex: Many people believe that, deep in the forest where Tranquill live, there is a peaceful place where there is no war.

name: Unfezant
pokedex: Males have plumage on their heads. They will never let themselves feel close to anyone other than their Trainers.

name: Blitzle
pokedex: When thunderclouds cover the sky, it will appear. It can catch lightning with its mane and store the electricity.

name: Zebstrika
pokedex: This ill-tempered Pokémon is dangerous because when it's angry, it shoots lightning from its mane in all directions.

name: Roggenrola
pokedex: They were discovered a hundred years ago in an earthquake fissure. Inside each one is an energy core.

name: Boldore
pokedex: Because its energy was too great to be contained, the energy leaked and formed orange crystals.

name: Gigalith
pokedex: The solar energy absorbed by its body's orange crystals is magnified internally and fired from its mouth.

name: Woobat
pokedex: Suction from its nostrils enables it to stick to cave walls during sleep. It leaves a heart-shaped mark behind.

name: Swoobat
pokedex: Anyone who comes into contact with the ultrasonic waves emitted by a courting male experiences a positive mood shift.

name: Drilbur
pokedex: It makes its way swiftly through the soil by putting both claws together and rotating at high speed.

name: Excadrill
pokedex: More than 300 feet below the surface, they build mazelike nests. Their activity can be destructive to subway tunnels.

name: Audino
pokedex: Its auditory sense is astounding. It has a radar-like ability to understand its surrounding through slight sounds.

name: Timburr
pokedex: These Pokémon appear at building sites and help out with construction. They always carry squared logs.

name: Gurdurr
pokedex: They strengthen their bodies by carrying steel beams. They show off their big muscles to their friends.

name: Conkeldurr
pokedex: They use concrete pillars as walking canes. They know moves that enable them to swing the pillars freely in battle.

name: Tympole
pokedex: By vibrating its cheeks, it emits sound waves imperceptible to humans. It uses the rhythm of these sounds to talk.

name: Palpitoad
pokedex: It lives in the water and on land. It uses its long, sticky tongue to capture prey.

name: Seismitoad
pokedex: It increases the power of its punches by vibrating the bumps on its fists. It can turn a boulder to rubble with one punch.

name: Throh
pokedex: When they encounter foes bigger than themselves, they try to throw them. They always travel in packs of five.

name: Sawk
pokedex: Tying their belts gets them pumped and makes their punches more destructive. Disturbing their training angers them.

name: Sewaddle
pokedex: This Pokémon makes clothes for itself. It chews up leaves and sews them with sticky thread extruded from its mouth.

name: Swadloon
pokedex: It protects itself from the cold by wrapping up in leaves. It stays on the move, eating leaves in forests.

name: Leavanny
pokedex: It keeps its eggs warm with heat from fermenting leaves. It also uses leaves to make warm wrappings for Sewaddle.

name: Venipede
pokedex: It discovers what is going on around it by using the feelers on its head and tail. It is brutally aggresive.

name: Whirlipede
pokedex: It is usually motionless, but when attacked, it rotates at high speed and then crashes into its opponent.

name: Scolipede
pokedex: Highly aggressive, it uses the claws near its neck to dig into its opponents and poison them.

name: Cottonee
pokedex: They go wherever the wind takes them. On rainy days, their bodies are heavier, so they take shelter beneath big trees.

name: Whimsicott
pokedex: Riding whirlwinds, they appear. These Pokémon sneak through gaps into houses and cause all sorts of mischief.

name: Petilil
pokedex: Since they prefer moist, nutrient-rich soil, the areas where Petilil live are known to be good for growing plants.

name: Lilligant
pokedex: The fragrance of the garland on its head has a relaxing effect. It withers if a Trainer does not take good care of it.

name: Basculin
pokedex: Savage, violent Pokémon, red and blue Basculin are always fighting each other over territory.

name: Sandile
pokedex: It moves along below the sand's surface, except for its nose and eyes. A dark membrane shields its eyes from the sun.

name: Krokorok
pokedex: The special membrane covering its eyes can sense the heat of objects, so it can see its surroundings, even in darkness.

name: Krookodile
pokedex: It can expand the focus of its eyes, enabling it to see objects in the far distance as if it were using binoculars.

name: Darumaka
pokedex: Darumaka's droppings are hot, so people used to put them in their clothes to keep themselves warm.

name: Darmanitan
pokedex: When weakened in battle, it transforms into a stone statue. Then it sharpens its mind and fights on mentally.

name: Maractus
pokedex: Arid regions are their habitat. They move rhythmically, making a sound similar to maracas.

name: Dwebble
pokedex: It makes a hole in a suitable rock. If that rock breaks, the Pokémon remains agitated until it locates a replacement.

name: Crustle
pokedex: It possesses legs of enormous strength, enabling it to carry heavy slabs for many days, even when crossing arid land.

name: Scraggy
pokedex: It immediately headbutts anyone that makes eye contact with it. Its skull is massively thick.

name: Scrafty
pokedex: It can smash concrete blocks with its kicking attacks. The one with the biggest crest is the group leader.

name: Sigilyph
pokedex: The guardians of an ancient city, they use their psychic power to attack enemies that invade their territory.

name: Yamask
pokedex: These Pokémon arose from the spirits of people interred in graves in past ages. Each retains memories of its former life.

name: Cofagrigus
pokedex: They pretend to be elaborate coffins to teach lessons to grave robbers. Their bodies are covered in pure gold.

name: Tirtouga
pokedex: About 100 million years ago, these Pokémon swam in oceans. It is thought they also went on land to attack prey.

name: Carracosta
pokedex: Incredible jaw strength enables them to chew up steel beams and rocks along with their prey.

name: Archen
pokedex: Revived from a fossil, this Pokémon is thought to be the ancestor of all bird Pokémon.

name: Archeops
pokedex: It runs better than it flies. It catches prey by running at speeds comparable to those of an automobile.

name: Trubbish
pokedex: The combination of garbage bags and industrial waste caused the chemical reaction that crated this Pokémon.

name: Garbodor
pokedex: They absorb garbage and make it part of their bodies. They shoot a poisonous liquid from their right-hand fingertips.

name: Zorua
pokedex: To protect themselves from danger, they hide their true identities by transforming into people and Pokémon.

name: Zoroark
pokedex: Each has the ability to fool a large group of people simultaneously. They protect their lair with illusory scenery.

name: Minccino
pokedex: These Pokémon prefer a tidy habitat. They are always sweeping and dusting, using their tails as brooms.

name: Cinccino
pokedex: Their white fur feels amazing to touch. Their fur repels dust and prevents static electricity from building up.

name: Gothita
pokedex: They intently observe both Trainers and Pokémon. Apparently, they are looking at something that only Gothita can see.

name: Gothorita
pokedex: Starlight is the source of their power. At night, they mark star positions by using psychic power to float stones.

name: Gothitelle
pokedex: They can predict the future from the placement and movement of the stars. They can see Trainers' life spans.

name: Solosis
pokedex: Because their bodies are enveloped in a special liquid, they can survive in any environment.

name: Duosion
pokedex: When their brains, now divided in two, are thinking the same thoughts, these Pokémon exhibit their maximum power.

name: Reuniclus
pokedex: These remarkably intelligent Pokémon fight by controlling arms that can grip with rock-crushing power.

name: Ducklett
pokedex: When attacked, it uses its feathers to splash water, escaping under cover of the spray.

name: Swanna
pokedex: It administers sharp, powerful pecks with its bill. It whips its long neck to deliver forceful repeated strikes.

name: Vanillite
pokedex: This Pokémon formed from icicles bathed in energy from the morning sun. It sleeps buried in snow.

name: Vanillish
pokedex: It conceals itself from enemy eyes by creating many small ice particles and hiding among them.

name: Vanilluxe
pokedex: If both heads get angry simultaneously, this Pokémon expels a blizzard, burying everything in snow.

name: Deerling
pokedex: The turning of the seasons changes the color and scent of this Pokémon's fur. People use it to mark the seasons.

name: Sawsbuck
pokedex: The plants growing on its horns change according to the season. The leaders of the herd possess magnificent horns.

name: Emolga
pokedex: They live on treetops and glide using the inside of a cape-like membrane while discharging electricity.

name: Karrablast
pokedex: When they feel threatened, they spit an acidic liquid to drive attackers away. This Pokémon targets Shelmet.

name: Escavalier
pokedex: These Pokémon evolve by wearing the shell covering of a Shelmet. The steel armor protects their whole body.

name: Foongus
pokedex: For some reason, this Pokémon resembles a Poké Ball. They release poison spores to repel those who try to catch them.

name: Amoonguss
pokedex: They show off their Poké Ball caps to lure prey, but very few Pokémon are fooled by this.

name: Frillish
pokedex: They paralyze prey with poison, then drag them down to their lairs, five miles below the surface.

name: Jellicent
pokedex: They propel themselves by expelling absorbed seawater from their bodies. Their favorite food is life energy.

name: Alomomola
pokedex: Floating in the open sea is how they live. When they find a wounded Pokémon, they embrace it and bring it to shore.

name: Joltik
pokedex: They attach themselves to large-bodied Pokémon and absorb static electricity, which they store in an electric pouch.

name: Galvantula
pokedex: They employ an electrically charged web to trap their prey. While it is immobilized by shock, they leisurely consume it.

name: Ferroseed
pokedex: They stick their spikes into cave walls and absorb the minerals they find in the rock.

name: Ferrothorn
pokedex: They attach themselves to cave ceilings, firing steel spikes at targets passing beneath them.

name: Klink
pokedex: Interlocking two bodies and spinning around generates the energy they need to live.

name: Klang
pokedex: Spinning minigears are rotated at high speed and repeatedly fired away. It is dangerous if the gears don't return.

name: Klinklang
pokedex: The gear with the red core is rotated at high speed for a rapid energy charge.

name: Tynamo
pokedex: These Pokémon move in schools. They have an electricity-generating organ, so they discharge electricity if in danger.

name: Eelektrik
pokedex: These Pokémon have a big appetite. When they spot their prey, they attack it and paralyze it with electricity.

name: Eelektross
pokedex: With their sucker mouths, they suck in prey. Then they use their fangs to shock the prey with electricity.

name: Elgyem
pokedex: This Pokémon had never been seen until it appeared from far in the desert 50 years ago.

name: Beheeyem
pokedex: It uses psychic power to control an opponent's brain and tamper with its memories.

name: Litwick
pokedex: While shining a light and pretending to be a guide, it leeches off the life force of any who follow it.

name: Lampent
pokedex: It arrives near the moment of death and steals spirit from the body.

name: Chandelure
pokedex: Being consumed in Chandelure's flame burns up the spirit, leaving the body behind.

name: Axew
pokedex: They mark their territory by leaving gashes in trees with their tusks. If a tusk breaks, a new one grows in quickly.

name: Fraxure
pokedex: Their tusks can shatter rocks. Territory battles between Fraxure can be intensely violent.

name: Haxorus
pokedex: Their sturdy tusks will stay sharp even if used to cut steel beams. These Pokémon are covered in hard armor.

name: Cubchoo
pokedex: Its nose is always running. It sniffs the snot back up because the mucus provides the raw material for its moves.

name: Beartic
pokedex: It freezes its breath to create fangs and claws of ice to fight with. Cold northern areas are its habitat.

name: Cryogonal
pokedex: They are born in snow clouds. They use chains made of ice crystals to capture prey.

name: Shelmet
pokedex: It evolves when bathed in an electric-like energy along with Karrablast. The reason is still unknown.

name: Accelgor
pokedex: Having removed its heavy shell, it becomes very light and can fight with ninja-like movements.

name: Stunfisk
pokedex: It conceals itself in the mud of the seashore. Then it waits. When prey touch it, it delivers a jolt of energy.

name: Mienfoo
pokedex: They have mastered elegant combos. As they concentrate, their battle moves become swifter and more precise.

name: Mienshao
pokedex: They use the long fur on their arms as a whip to strike their opponents.

name: Druddigon
pokedex: It races through narrow caves, using its sharp claws to catch prey. Then skin on its face is harder than a rock.

name: Golett
pokedex: These Pokémon are thought to have been created by the science of an ancient and mysterious civilization.

name: Golurk
pokedex: It is said that Golurk were ordered to protect people and Pokémon by the ancient people who made them.

name: Pawniard
pokedex: They fight at Bisharp's command. They cling to their prey and inflict damage by sinking their blades into it.

name: Bisharp
pokedex: Bisharp pursues prey in the company of a large group of Pawniard. Then Bisharp finishes off the prey.

name: Bouffalant
pokedex: They charge wildly and headbutt everything. They headbutts have enough destructive force to derail a train.

name: Rufflet
pokedex: They will challenge anything, even strong opponents, without fear. Their frequent fights help them become stronger.

name: Braviary
pokedex: The more scars they have, the more respect these brave soldiers of the sky get from their peers.

name: Vullaby
pokedex: They tend to guard their posteriors with suitable bones they have found. They pursue weak Pokémon.

name: Mandibuzz
pokedex: Watching from the sky, they swoop to strike weakened Pokémon on the ground. They decorate themselves with bones.

name: Heatmor
pokedex: Using their very hot, flame-covered tongues, they burn through Durant's steel bodies and consume their insides.

name: Durant
pokedex: Durant dig nests in mountains. They build their complicated, interconnected tunnels in mazes.

name: Deino
pokedex: They cannot see, so they tackle and bite to learn about their surroundings. Their bodies are covered in wounds.

name: Zweilous
pokedex: Since their two heads do not get along and compete with each other for food, they always eat too much.

name: Hydreigon
pokedex: The heads on their arms do not have brains. They use all three heads to consume and destroy everything.

name: Larvesta
pokedex: The base of volcanoes is where they make their homes. They shoot fire from their five horns to repel attacking enemies.

name: Volcarona
pokedex: A sea of fire engulfs the surroundings of their battles, since they use their six wings to scatter their ember scales.

name: Cobalion
pokedex: It has a body and heart of steel. Its glare is sufficient to make even an unruly Pokémon obey it.

name: Terrakion
pokedex: Its charge is strong enough to break through a giant castle wall in one blow. This Pokémon is spoken of in legends.

name: Virizion
pokedex: Its head sprouts horns as sharp as blades. Using whirlwind-like movements, it confounds and swiftly cuts opponents.

name: Tornadus
pokedex: Tornadus expels massive energy from its tail, causing severe storms. Its power is great enough to blow houses away.

name: Thundurus
pokedex: The spikes on its tail discharge immense bolts of lightning. It flies around the Unova region firing off lightning bolts.

name: Reshiram
pokedex: When Reshiram's tail flares, the heat energy moves the atmosphere and changes the world's weather.

name: Zekrom
pokedex: This Pokémon appears in legends. In its tail, it has a giant generator that creates electricity.

name: Landorus
pokedex: The energy that comes pouring from its tail increases the nutrition in the soil, making crops grow to great size.

name: Kyurem
pokedex: It generates a powerful, freezing energy inside itself, but its body became frozen when the energy leaked out.

name: Keldeo
pokedex: It crosses the world, running over the surfaces of oceans and rivers. It appears at scenic waterfronts.

name: Meloetta
pokedex: Many famous songs have been inspired by the melodies that Meloetta plays.

name: Genesect
pokedex: This ancient bug Pokémon was altered by Team Plasma. They upgraded the cannon on its back.

name: Chespin
pokedex: The quills on its head are usually soft. When it flexes them, the points become so hard and sharp that they can pierce rock.

name: Quilladin
pokedex: They strengthen their lower bodies by running into one another. They are very kind and won't start fights.

name: Chesnaught
pokedex: Its Tackle is forceful enough to flip a 50-ton tank. It shields its allies from danger with its own body.

name: Fennekin
pokedex: As it walks, it munches on a twig in place of a snack. It intimidates opponents by puffing hot air out of its ears.

name: Braixen
pokedex: When the twig is plucked from its tail, friction sets the twig alight. The flame is used to send signals to its allies.

name: Delphox
pokedex: It gazes into the flame at the tip of its branch to achieve a focused state, which allows it to see into the future.

name: Froakie
pokedex: It protects its skin by covering its body in delicate bubbles. Beneath its happy-go-lucky air, it keeps a watchful eye on its surroundings.

name: Frogadier
pokedex: It can throw bubble-covered pebbles with precise control, hitting empty cans up to a hundred feet away.

name: Greninja
pokedex: It appears and vanishes with a ninja's grace. It toys with its enemies using swift movements, while slicing them with throwing stars of sharpest water.

name: Bunnelby
pokedex: It has ears like shovels. Digging holes strengthens its ears so much that they can sever thick roots effortlessly.

name: Diggersby
pokedex: As powerful as an excavator, its ears can reduce dense bedrock to rubble. When it's finished digging, it lounges lazily.

name: Fletchling
pokedex: These friendly Pokémon send signals to one another with beautiful chirps and tail-feather movements.

name: Fletchinder
pokedex: From its beak, it expels embers that set the tall grass on fire. Then it pounces on the bewildered prey that pop out of the grass.

name: Talonflame
pokedex: In the fever of an exciting battle, it showers embers from the gaps between its feathers and takes to the air.

name: Scatterbug
pokedex: When under attack from bird Pokémon, it spews a poisonous black powder that causes paralysis on contact.

name: Spewpa
pokedex: It lives hidden within thicket shadows. When predators attack, it quickly bristles the fur covering its body in an effort to threaten them.

name: Vivillon
pokedex: Vivillon with many different patterns are found all over the world. These patterns are affected by the climate of their habitat.

name: Litleo
pokedex: They set off on their own from their pride and live by themselves to become stronger. These hot-blooded Pokémon are quick to fight.

name: Pyroar
pokedex: With fiery breath of more than 6,000 degrees Celsius, they viciously threaten any challenger. The females protect the pride's cubs.

name: Flabébé
pokedex: When it finds a flower it likes, it dwells on that flower its whole life long. It floats in the wind's embrace with an untroubled heart.

name: Floette
pokedex: It flutters around fields of flowers and cares for flowers that are starting to wilt. It draws out the power of flowers to battle.

name: Florges
pokedex: It claims exquisite flower gardens as its territory, and it obtains power from basking in the energy emitted by flowering plants.

name: Skiddo
pokedex: If it has sunshine and water, it doesn't need to eat, because it can generate energy from the leaves on its back.

name: Gogoat
pokedex: It can tell how its trainer is feeling by subtle shifts in the grip on its horns. This empathetic sense lets them run as if one being.

name: Pancham
pokedex: It does its best to be taken seriously by its enemies, but its glare is not sufficiently intimidating. Chewing on a leaf is its trademark.

name: Pangoro
pokedex: It charges ahead and bashes its opponents like a berserker, uncaring about any hits it might take. Its arms are mighty enough to snap a telephone pole.

name: Furfrou
pokedex: Trimming its fluffy fur not only makes it more elegant but also increases the swiftness of its movements.

name: Espurr
pokedex: The organ that emits its intense psychic power is sheltered by its ears to keep power from leaking out.

name: Meowstic
pokedex: Revealing the eyelike patterns on the insides of its ears will unleash its psychic powers. It normally keeps the patterns hidden, however.

name: Honedge
pokedex: Apparently this Pokémon is born when a departed spirit inhabits a sword. It attaches itself to people and drinks their life force.

name: Doublade
pokedex: The complex attack patterns of its two swords are unstoppable, even for an opponent greatly accomplished at swordplay.

name: Aegislash
pokedex: In this defensive stance, Aegislash uses its steel body and a force field of spectral power to reduce the damage of any attack.

name: Spritzee
pokedex: It emits a scent that enraptures those who smell it. This fragrance changes depending on what it has eaten.

name: Aromatisse
pokedex: It devises various scents, pleasant and unpleasant, and emits scents that its enemies dislike in order to gain an edge in battle.

name: Swirlix
pokedex: To entangle its opponents in battle, it extrudes white threads as sweet and sticky as cotton candy.

name: Slurpuff
pokedex: It can distinguish the faintest of scents. It puts its sensitive sense of smell to use by helping pastry chefs in their work.

name: Inkay
pokedex: It flashes the light-emitting spots on its body, which drains its opponent's will to fight. It takes the opportunity to scuttle away and hide.

name: Malamar
pokedex: It lures prey close with hypnotic motions, then wraps its tentacles around it before finishing it off with digestive fluids.

name: Binacle
pokedex: They stretch and then contract, yanking their rocks along with them in bold hops. They eat seaweed that washes up on the shoreline.

name: Barbaracle
pokedex: Barbaracle's legs and hands have minds of their own, and they will move independently. But they usually follow the head's orders.

name: Skrelp
pokedex: Camouflaged as rotten kelp, they spray liquid poison on prey that approaches unawares and then finish it off.

name: Dragalge
pokedex: Their poison is strong enough to eat through the hull of a tanker, and they spit it indiscriminately at anything that enters their territory.

name: Clauncher
pokedex: Through controlled expulsions of internal gas, it can expel water like a pistol shot. At close distances, it can shatter rock.

name: Clawitzer
pokedex: By expelling water from the nozzle in the back of its claw, it can move at a speed of 60 knots.

name: Helioptile
pokedex: They make their home in deserts. They can generate their energy from basking in the sun, so eating food is not a requirement.

name: Heliolisk
pokedex: They flare their frills and generate energy. A single Heliolisk can generate sufficient electricity to power a skyscraper.

name: Tyrunt
pokedex: Its immense jaws have enough destructive force that it can chew up an automobile. It lived 100 million years ago.

name: Tyrantrum
pokedex: Thanks to its gargantuan jaws, which could shred thick metal plates as if they were paper, it was invincible in the ancient world it once inhabited.

name: Amaura
pokedex: This ancient Pokémon was restored from part of its body that had been frozen in ice for over 100 million years.

name: Aurorus
pokedex: Using its diamond-shaped crystals, it can instantly create a wall of ice to block an opponent's attack.

name: Sylveon
pokedex: Its ribbonlike feelers give off an aura that weakens hostility in its prey, causing them to let down their guard. Then it attacks.

name: Hawlucha
pokedex: With its wings, it controls its position in the air. It likes to attack from above, a maneuver that is difficult to defend against.

name: Dedenne
pokedex: Its whiskers serve as antennas. By sending and receiving electrical waves, it can communicate with others over vast distances.

name: Carbink
pokedex: Born from the high temperatures and pressures deep underground, it defends itself by firing beams from the jewel part of its body.

name: Goomy
pokedex: Its source of protection is its slimy, germ-laden mucous membrane. Anyone who touches it needs some thorough hand-washing.

name: Sliggoo
pokedex: This Pokémon's mucous can dissolve anything. Toothless, it sprays mucous on its prey. Once they're nicely dissolved, it slurps them up.

name: Goodra
pokedex: It gets picked on because it's meek. But then, whoever teased it gets to feel the full force of its horns and a good swatting from its thick tail.

name: Klefki
pokedex: It never lets go of a key that it likes, so people give it the keys to vaults and safes as a way to prevent crime.

name: Phantump
pokedex: These Pokémon are stumps possessed by the spirits of children who died in the forest. Their cries sound like eerie screams.

name: Trevenant
pokedex: Through its roots, it exerts control over other trees. A deadly curse falls upon anyone cutting down trees in forests where Trevenant dwell.

name: Pumpkaboo
pokedex: When taking spirits to the afterlife, small Pumpkaboo prefer the spirits of children to those of adults.

name: Gourgeist
pokedex: Small Gourgeist pretend to be children to fool adults. Anyone who falls for the act gets carried away to the hereafter.

name: Bergmite
pokedex: It blocks opponents' attacks with the ice that shields its body. It uses cold air to repair any cracks with new ice.

name: Avalugg
pokedex: Its ice-covered body is as hard as steel. Its cumbersome frame crushes anything that stands in its way.

name: Noibat
pokedex: Even a robust wrestler will become dizzy and unable to stand when exposed to its 200,000-hertz ultrasonic waves.

name: Noivern
pokedex: They fly around on moonless nights and attack careless prey. Nothing can beat them in a battle in the dark.

name: Xerneas
pokedex: Legends say it can share eternal life. It slept for a thousand years in the form of a tree before its revival.

name: Yveltal
pokedex: When its life comes to an end, it absorbs the life energy of every living thing and turns into a cocoon once more.

name: Zygarde
pokedex: It's thought to be monitoring the ecosystem. There are rumors that even greater power lies hidden within it.

name: Diancie
pokedex: A sudden transformation of Carbink, its pink, glimmering body is said to be the loveliest sight in the whole world.

name: Hoopa
pokedex: This troublemaker sends anything and everything to faraway places using its loop, which can warp space.

name: Volcanion
pokedex: It lets out billows of steam and disappears into the dense fog. It's said to live in mountains where humans do not tread.

name: Rowlet
pokedex: It sends its feathers, which are as sharp as blades, flying in attack. Its legs are strong, so its kicks are also formidable.

name: Dartrix
pokedex: A bit of a dandy, it spends its free time preening its wings. Its preoccupation with any dirt on its plumage can leave it unable to battle.

name: Decidueye
pokedex: It fires arrow quills from its wings with such precision, they can pierce a pebble at distances over a hundred yards.

name: Litten
pokedex: Its coat regrows twice a year. When the time comes, Litten sets its own body on fire and burns away the old fur.

name: Torracat
pokedex: It can act spoiled if it grows close to its Trainer. A powerful Pokémon, its sharp claws can leave its Trainer's whole body covered in scratches.

name: Incineroar
pokedex: Although it's rough mannered and egotistical, it finds beating down unworthy opponents boring. It gets motivated for stronger opponents.

name: Popplio
pokedex: This Pokémon snorts body fluids from its nose, blowing balloons to smash into its foes. It's famous for being a hard worker.

name: Brionne
pokedex: It gets excited when it sees a dance it doesn't know. This hard worker practices diligently until it can learn that dance.

name: Primarina
pokedex: It controls its water balloons with song. The melody is learned from others of its kind and is passed down from one generation to the next.

name: Pikipek
pokedex: It pecks at trees with its hard beak. You can get some idea of its mood or condition from the rhythm of its pecking.

name: Trumbeak
pokedex: It eats berries and stores their seeds in its beak. When it encounters enemies or prey, it fires off all the seeds in a burst.

name: Toucannon
pokedex: They smack beaks with others of their kind to communicate. The strength and number of hits tell each other how they feel.

name: Yungoos
pokedex: Its stomach takes up most of its long torso. It's a big eater, so the amount Trainers have to spend on its food is no laughing matter.

name: Gumshoos
pokedex: When it finds a trace of its prey, it patiently stakes out the location... but it's always snoozing by nightfall.

name: Grubbin
pokedex: It spits a sticky thread to stop opponents in their tracks, and then it grabs them in its sharp, sturdy mandibles to take them down.

name: Charjabug
pokedex: It buries itself in fallen leaves and barely moves, munching away on humus. If you accidentally step on one, you'll get a shock!

name: Vikavolt
pokedex: It zips around, on sharp lookout for an opening. It concentrates electrical energy within its large jaws and uses it to zap its enemies.

name: Crabrawler
pokedex: It punches so much, its pincers often come off from overuse, but they grow back quickly. What little meat they contain is rich and delicious.

name: Crabominable
pokedex: It aimed for the top but got lost and ended up on a snowy mountain. Being forced to endure the cold, this Pokémon evolved and grew fur.

name: Oricorio
pokedex: It beats its wings together to create fire. As it moves in the steps of its beautiful dance, it bathes opponents in intense flames.

name: Cutiefly
pokedex: It feeds on the nectar and pollen of flowers. Because it's able to sense auras, it can identify which flowers are about to bloom.

name: Ribombee
pokedex: Rain makes pollen damp, so Ribombee hates rain. When it sees ominous clouds, it finds a hollow in a tree, where it waits stock-still.

name: Rockruff
pokedex: This Pokémon has lived with people since times long ago. It can sense when its Trainer is in the dumps and will stick close by its Trainer's side.

name: Lycanroc
pokedex: Its quick movements confuse its enemies. Well equipped with claws and fangs, it also uses the sharp rocks in its mane as weapons.

name: Wishiwashi
pokedex: It's awfully weak and notably tasty, so everyone is always out to get it. As it happens, anyone trying to bully it receives a painful lesson.

name: Mareanie
pokedex: It plunges the poison spike on its head into its prey. When the prey has weakened, Mareanie deals the finishing blow with its 10 tentacles.

name: Toxapex
pokedex: Those attacked by Toxapex's poison will suffer intense pain for three days and three nights. Post-recovery, there will be some aftereffects.

name: Mudbray
pokedex: It loves playing in the mud. If it isn't showered with mud on a daily basis, it gets stressed out and stops listening to its Trainer.

name: Mudsdale
pokedex: It remains calm and unmoving no matter the situation. It mixes dirt with the saliva in its mouth to make a special kind of mud.

name: Dewpider
pokedex: When two Dewpider meet, they display their water bubbles to each other. Then the one with the smaller bubble gets out of the other's way.

name: Araquanid
pokedex: It delivers headbutts with the water bubble on its head. Small Pokémon get sucked into the bubble, where they drown.

name: Fomantis
pokedex: When the sun rises, Fomantis spreads its four leaves and bathes in the sunlight. The tip of its head has a pleasant aroma.

name: Lurantis
pokedex: It requires a lot of effort to maintain Lurantis's vivid coloring, but some collectors enjoy this work and treat it as their hobby.

name: Morelull
pokedex: It scatters its shining spores around itself. Even though they're dangerous, nighttime tours of forests where Morelull live are popular.

name: Shiinotic
pokedex: It puts its prey to sleep and siphons off their vitality through the tip of its arms. If one of its kind is weakened, it helps by sending it vitality.

name: Salandit
pokedex: It burns its bodily fluids to create a poisonous gas. When its enemies become disoriented from inhaling the gas, it attacks them.

name: Salazzle
pokedex: Filled with pheromones, its poisonous gas can be diluted to use in the production of luscious perfumes.

name: Stufful
pokedex: Despite its adorable appearance, when it gets angry and flails about, its arms and legs could knock a pro wrestler sprawling.

name: Bewear
pokedex: It waves its hands wildly in intimidation and warning. Life is over for anyone who doesn't run away as fast as possible.

name: Bounsweet
pokedex: Because of its sweet, delicious aroma, bird Pokémon are always after it, but it's not intelligent enough to care.

name: Steenee
pokedex: It's protected by its hard sepals, so it plays with bird Pokémon without worry. They peck it relentlessly, but it doesn't care.

name: Tsareena
pokedex: A Pokémon with an aggressive personality and a mastery of kicking, it cackles every time it kicks an opponent.

name: Comfey
pokedex: Baths prepared with the flowers from its vine have a relaxing effect, so this Pokémon is a hit with many people.

name: Oranguru
pokedex: It normally spends its time meditating in the treetops. It throws Poké Balls and gives other Pokémon orders as it pleases.

name: Passimian
pokedex: Berries are its weapons as well as the staple of its diet. The one that can throw a berry the farthest is the boss of the troop.

name: Wimpod
pokedex: This Pokémon is a coward. As it desperately dashes off, the flailing of its many legs leaves a sparkling clean path in its wake.

name: Golisopod
pokedex: It battles skillfully with its six arms, but spends most of its time peacefully meditating in caves deep beneath the sea.

name: Sandygast
pokedex: It likes the shovel on its head, so Sandygast will get serious and fight any children who come to take it back.

name: Palossand
pokedex: Buried beneath the castle are masses of dried-up bones from those whose vitality it has drained.

name: Pyukumuku
pokedex: It lives in shallow seas, such as areas near a beach. It can eject its internal organs, which it uses to engulf its prey or battle enemies.

name: Type: Null
pokedex: The heavy control mask it wears suppresses its intrinsic capabilities. This Pokémon has some hidden special power.

name: Silvally
pokedex: Its trust in its partner is what awakens it. This Pokémon is capable of changing its type, a flexibility that is well displayed in battle.

name: Minior
pokedex: Originally making its home in the ozone layer, it hurtles to the ground when the shell enclosing its body grows too heavy.

name: Komala
pokedex: It remains asleep from birth to death as a result of the sedative properties of the leaves that form its diet.

name: Turtonator
pokedex: It lives in volcanoes and eats sulfur and other minerals. Materials from the food it eats form the basis of its explosive shell.

name: Togedemaru
pokedex: The long hairs on its back act as lightning rods. The bolts of lightning it attracts are stored as energy in its electric sac.

name: Mimikyu
pokedex: A lonely Pokémon, it conceals its terrifying appearance beneath an old rag so it can get closer to people and other Pokémon.

name: Bruxish
pokedex: When it unleashes its psychic power from the protuberance on its head, the grating sound of grinding teeth echoes through the area.

name: Drampa
pokedex: This Pokémon is friendly to people and loves children most of all. It comes from deep in the mountains to play with children it likes in town.

name: Dhelmise
pokedex: The soul of seaweed adrift in the waves became reborn as this Pokémon. It maintains itself with new infusions of seabed detritus and seaweed.

name: Jangmo-o
pokedex: It expresses its feelings by smacking its scales. Metallic sounds echo through the tall mountains where Jangmo-o lives.

name: Hakamo-o
pokedex: It sheds and regrows its scales on a continuous basis. The scales become harder and sharper each time they're regrown.

name: Kommo-o
pokedex: Its rigid scales function as offense and defense. In the past, its scales were processed and used to make weapons and other commodities.

name: Tapu Koko
pokedex: Although it's called a guardian deity, if a person or Pokémon puts it in a bad mood, it will become a malevolent deity and attack.

name: Tapu Lele
pokedex: As it flutters about, it scatters its strangely glowing scales. Touching them is said to restore good health on the spot.

name: Tapu Bulu
pokedex: It pulls large trees up by the roots and swings them around. It causes vegetation to grow, and then it absorbs energy from the growth.

name: Tapu Fini
pokedex: The dense fog it creates brings the downfall and destruction of its confused enemies. Ocean currents are the source of its energy.

name: Cosmog
pokedex: Whether or not it's a Pokémon from this world is a mystery. When it's in a jam, it warps away to a safe place to hide.

name: Cosmoem
pokedex: Motionless as if dead, its body is faintly warm to the touch. In the distant past, it was called the cocoon of the stars.

name: Solgaleo
pokedex: It is said to live in another world. The intense light it radiates from the surface of its body can make the darkest of nights light up like midday.

name: Lunala
pokedex: Said to live in another world, this Pokémon devours light, drawing the moonless dark veil of night over the brightness of day.

name: Nihilego
pokedex: One of several mysterious Ultra Beasts. People on the street report observing those infested by it suddenly becoming violent.

name: Buzzwole
pokedex: This Ultra Beast appeared from another world. It shows off its body, but whether that display is a boast or a threat remains unclear.

name: Pheromosa
pokedex: One of the Ultra Beasts. It refuses to touch anything, perhaps because it senses some uncleanness in this world.

name: Xurkitree
pokedex: One of the mysterious life-forms known as Ultra Beasts. Astonishing electric shocks emanate from its entire body, according to witnesses.

name: Celesteela
pokedex: One kind of Ultra Beast. Witnesses have seen it burn down a forest by expelling gas from its two arms.

name: Kartana
pokedex: One of the Ultra Beast life-forms, it was observed cutting down a gigantic steel tower with one stroke of its blade.

name: Guzzlord
pokedex: A dangerous Ultra Beast, it appears to be eating constantly, but for some reason its droppings have never been found.

name: Necrozma
pokedex: Light is apparently the source of its energy. It has an extraordinarily vicious disposition and is constantly firing off laser beams.

name: Magearna
pokedex: This artificial Pokémon, constructed more than 500 years ago, can understand human speech but cannot itself speak.

name: Marshadow
pokedex: Able to conceal itself in shadows, it never appears before humans, so its very existence was the stuff of myth.

name: Poipole
pokedex: An Ultra Beast that lives in a different world, it cackles wildly as it sprays its opponents with poison from the needles on its head.

name: Naganadel
pokedex: One kind of Ultra Beast, it fires a glowing, venomous liquid from its needles. This liquid is also immensely adhesive.

name: Stakataka
pokedex: When stone walls started moving and attacking, the brute's true identity was this mysterious life-form, which brings to mind an Ultra Beast.

name: Blacephalon
pokedex: It slithers toward people. Then, without warning, it triggers the explosion of its own head. It's apparently one kind of Ultra Beast.

name: Zeraora
pokedex: It approaches its enemies at the speed of lightning, then tears them limb from limb with its sharp claws.

name: Meltan
pokedex: It melts particles of iron and other metals found in the subsoil, so it can absorb them into its body of molten steel.

name: Melmetal
pokedex: Revered long ago for its capacity to create iron from nothing, for some reason it has come back to life after 3,000 years.

name: Grookey
pokedex: When it uses its special stick to strike up a beat, the sound waves produced carry revitalizing energy to the plants and flowers in the area.

name: Thwackey
pokedex: When it's drumming out rapid beats in battle, it gets so caught up in the rhythm that it won't even notice that it's already knocked out its opponent.

name: Rillaboom
pokedex: By drumming, it taps into the power of its special tree stump. The roots of the stump follow its direction in battle.

name: Scorbunny
pokedex: A warm-up of running around gets fire energy coursing through this Pokémon's body. Once that happens, it's ready to fight at full power.

name: Raboot
pokedex: It kicks berries right off the branches of trees and then juggles them with its feet, practicing its footwork.

name: Cinderace
pokedex: It juggles a pebble with its feet, turning it into a burning soccer ball. Its shots strike opponents hard and leave them scorched.

name: Sobble
pokedex: When scared, this Pokémon cries. Its tears pack the chemical punch of 100 onions, and attackers won't be able to resist weeping.

name: Drizzile
pokedex: A clever combatant, this Pokémon battles using water balloons created with moisture secreted from its palms.

name: Inteleon
pokedex: It has many hidden capabilities, such as fingertips that can shoot water and a membrane on its back that it can use to glide through the air.

name: Skwovet
pokedex: It eats berries nonstop—a habit that has made it more resilient than it looks. It'll show up on farms, searching for yet more berries.

name: Greedent
pokedex: It stashes berries in its tail - so many berries that they fall out constantly. But this Pokémon is a bit slow-witted, so it doesn't notice the loss.

name: Rookidee
pokedex: Jumping nimbly about, this small-bodied Pokémon takes advantage of even the slightest opportunity to disorient larger opponents.

name: Corvisquire
pokedex: Smart enough to use tools in battle, these Pokémon have been seen picking up rocks and flinging them or using ropes to wrap up enemies.

name: Corviknight
pokedex: This Pokémon reigns supreme in the skies. The black luster of its steel body could drive terror into the heart of any foe.

name: Blipbug
pokedex: Often found in gardens, this Pokémon has hairs on its body that it uses to assess its surroundings.

name: Dottler
pokedex: It barely moves, but it's still alive. Hiding in its shell without food or water seems to have awakened its psychic powers.

name: Orbeetle
pokedex: It's famous for its high level of intelligence, and the large size of its brain is proof that it also possesses immense psychic power.

name: Nickit
pokedex: Aided by the soft pads on its feet, it silently raids the food stores of other Pokémon. It survives off its ill-gotten gains.

name: Thievul
pokedex: It secretly marks potential targets with a scent. By following the scent, it stalks its targets and steals from them when they least expect it.

name: Gossifleur
pokedex: It anchors itself in the ground with its single leg, then basks in the sun. After absorbing enough sunlight, its petals spread as it blooms brilliantly.

name: Eldegoss
pokedex: The seeds attached to its cotton fluff are full of nutrients. It spreads them on the wind so that plants and other Pokémon can benefit from them.

name: Wooloo
pokedex: Its curly fleece is such an effective cushion that this Pokémon could fall off a cliff and stand right back up at the bottom, unharmed.

name: Dubwool
pokedex: Its majestic horns are meant only to impress the opposite gender. They never see use in battle.

name: Chewtle
pokedex: It starts off battles by attacking with its rock-hard horn, but as soon as the opponent flinches, this Pokémon bites down and never lets go.

name: Drednaw
pokedex: With jaws that can shear through steel rods, this highly aggressive Pokémon chomps down on its unfortunate prey.

name: Yamper
pokedex: This gluttonous Pokémon only assists people with their work because it wants treats. As it runs, it crackles with electricity.

name: Boltund
pokedex: This Pokémon generates electricity and channels it into its legs to keep them going strong. Boltund can run nonstop for three full days.

name: Rolycoly
pokedex: Most of its body has the same composition as coal. Fittingly, this Pokémon was first discovered in coal mines about 400 years ago.

name: Carkol
pokedex: By rapidly rolling its legs, it can travel at over 18 mph. The temperature of the flames it breathes exceeds 1,000 degrees Celsius.

name: Coalossal
pokedex: While it's engaged in battle, its mountain of coal will burn bright red, sending off sparks that scorch the surrounding area.

name: Applin
pokedex: It spends its entire life inside an apple. It hides from its natural enemies, bird Pokémon, by pretending it's just an apple and nothing more.

name: Flapple
pokedex: It ate a sour apple, and that induced its evolution. In its cheeks, it stores an acid capable of causing chemical burns.

name: Appletun
pokedex: Its body is covered in sweet nectar, and the skin on its back is especially yummy. Children used to have it as a snack.

name: Silicobra
pokedex: It spews sand from its nostrils. While the enemy is blinded, it burrows into the ground to hide.

name: Sandaconda
pokedex: Its unique style of coiling allows it to blast sand out of its sand sac more efficiently.

name: Cramorant
pokedex: It's so strong that it can knock out some opponents in a single hit, but it also may forget what it's battling midfight.

name: Arrokuda
pokedex: If it sees any movement around it, this Pokémon charges for it straightaway, leading with its sharply pointed jaw. It's very proud of that jaw.

name: Barraskewda
pokedex: This Pokémon has a jaw that's as sharp as a spear and as strong as steel. Apparently Barraskewda's flesh is surprisingly tasty, too.

name: Toxel
pokedex: It manipulates the chemical makeup of its poison to produce electricity. The voltage is weak, but it can cause a tingling paralysis.

name: Toxtricity
pokedex: When this Pokémon sounds as if it's strumming a guitar, it's actually clawing at the protrusions on its chest to generate electricity.

name: Sizzlipede
pokedex: It stores flammable gas in its body and uses it to generate heat. The yellow sections on its belly get particularly hot.

name: Centiskorch
pokedex: While its burning body is already dangerous on its own, this excessively hostile Pokémon also has large and very sharp fangs.

name: Clobbopus
pokedex: It's very curious, but its means of investigating things is to try to punch them with its tentacles. The search for food is what brings it onto land.

name: Grapploct
pokedex: A body made up of nothing but muscle makes the grappling moves this Pokémon performs with its tentacles tremendously powerful.

name: Sinistea
pokedex: The teacup in which this Pokémon makes its home is a famous piece of antique tableware. Many forgeries are in circulation.

name: Polteageist
pokedex: This species lives in antique teapots. Most pots are forgeries, but on rare occasions, an authentic work is found.

name: Hatenna
pokedex: Via the protrusion on its head, it senses other creatures' emotions. If you don't have a calm disposition, it will never warm up to you.

name: Hattrem
pokedex: Using the braids on its head, it pummels foes to get them to quiet down. One blow from those braids would knock out a professional boxer.

name: Hatterene
pokedex: It emits psychic power strong enough to cause headaches as a deterrent to the approach of others.

name: Impidimp
pokedex: Through its nose, it sucks in the emanations produced by people and Pokémon when they feel annoyed. It thrives off this negative energy.

name: Morgrem
pokedex: With sly cunning, it tries to lure people into the woods. Some believe it to have the power to make crops grow.

name: Grimmsnarl
pokedex: Its hairs work like muscle fibers. When its hairs unfurl, they latch on to opponents, ensnaring them as tentacles would.

name: Obstagoon
pokedex: It evolved after experiencing numerous fights. While crossing its arms, it lets out a shout that would make any opponent flinch.

name: Perrserker
pokedex: What appears to be an iron helmet is actually hardened hair. This Pokémon lives for the thrill of battle.

name: Cursola
pokedex: Its shell is overflowing with its heightened otherworldly energy. The ectoplasm serves as protection for this Pokémon's core spirit.

name: Sirfetch'd
pokedex: After deflecting attacks with its hard leaf shield, it strikes back with its sharp leek stalk. The leek stalk is both weapon and food.

name: Mr. Rime
pokedex: Its amusing movements make it very popular. It releases its psychic power from the pattern on its belly.

name: Runerigus
pokedex: A powerful curse was woven into an ancient painting. After absorbing the spirit of a Yamask, the painting began to move.

name: Milcery
pokedex: This Pokémon was born from sweet-smelling particles in the air. Its body is made of cream.

name: Alcremie
pokedex: When Alcremie is content, the cream it secretes from its hands becomes sweeter and richer.

name: Falinks
pokedex: The six of them work together as one Pokémon. Teamwork is also their battle strategy, and they constantly change their formation as they fight.

name: Pincurchin
pokedex: It stores electricity in each spine. Even if one gets broken off, it still continues to emit electricity for at least three hours.

name: Snom
pokedex: It spits out thread imbued with a frigid sort of energy and uses it to tie its body to branches, disguising itself as an icicle while it sleeps.

name: Frosmoth
pokedex: It shows no mercy to any who desecrate fields and mountains. It will fly around on its icy wings, causing a blizzard to chase offenders away.

name: Stonjourner
pokedex: Once a year, on a specific date and at a specific time, they gather out of nowhere and form up in a circle.

name: Eiscue
pokedex: It drifted in on the flow of ocean waters from a frigid place. It keeps its head iced constantly to make sure it stays nice and cold.

name: Indeedee
pokedex: It uses the horns on its head to sense the emotions of others. Males will act as valets for those they serve, looking after their every need.

name: Morpeko
pokedex: As it eats the seeds stored up in its pocket-like pouches, this Pokémon is not just satisfying its constant hunger. It's also generating electricity.

name: Cufant
pokedex: It digs up the ground with its trunk. It's also very strong, being able to carry loads of over five tons without any problem at all.

name: Copperajah
pokedex: These Pokémon live in herds. Their trunks have incredible grip strength, strong enough to crush giant rocks into powder.

name: Dracozolt
pokedex: In ancient times, it was unbeatable thanks to its powerful lower body, but it went extinct anyway after it depleted all its plant-based food sources.

name: Arctozolt
pokedex: The shaking of its freezing upper half is what generates its electricity. It has a hard time walking around.

name: Dracovish
pokedex: Powerful legs and jaws made it the apex predator of its time. Its own overhunting of its prey was what drove it to extinction.

name: Arctovish
pokedex: Though it's able to capture prey by freezing its surroundings, it has trouble eating the prey afterward because its mouth is on top of its head.

name: Duraludon
pokedex: Its body resembles polished metal, and it's both lightweight and strong. The only drawback is that it rusts easily.

name: Dreepy
pokedex: After being reborn as a ghost Pokémon, Dreepy wanders the areas it used to inhabit back when it was alive in prehistoric seas.

name: Drakloak
pokedex: It's capable of flying faster than 120 mph. It battles alongside Dreepy and dotes on them until they successfully evolve.

name: Dragapult
pokedex: When it isn't battling, it keeps Dreepy in the holes on its horns. Once a fight starts, it launches the Dreepy like supersonic missiles.

name: Zacian
pokedex: Known as a legendary hero, this Pokémon absorbs metal particles, transforming them into a weapon it uses to battle.

name: Zamazenta
pokedex: This Pokémon slept for aeons while in the form of a statue. It was asleep for so long, people forgot that it ever existed.

name: Eternatus
pokedex: The core on its chest absorbs energy emanating from the lands of the Galar region. This energy is what allows Eternatus to stay active.

name: Kubfu
pokedex: Kubfu trains hard to perfect its moves. The moves it masters will determine which form it takes when it evolves.

name: Urshifu
pokedex: Inhabiting the mountains of a distant region, this Pokémon races across sheer cliffs, training its legs and refining its moves.

name: Zarude
pokedex: Once the vines on Zarude's body tear off, they become nutrients in the soil. This helps the plants of the forest grow.

name: Regieleki
pokedex: This Pokémon is a cluster of electrical energy. It's said that removing the rings on Regieleki's body will unleash the Pokémon's latent power.

name: Regidrago
pokedex: Its body is composed of crystallized dragon energy. Regidrago is said to have the powers of every dragon Pokémon.

name: Glastrier
pokedex: Glastrier has tremendous physical strength, and the mask of ice covering its face is 100 times harder than diamond.

name: Spectrier
pokedex: As it dashes through the night, Spectrier absorbs the life-force of sleeping creatures. It craves silence and solitude.

name: Calyrex
pokedex: Calyrex is a merciful Pokémon, capable of providing healing and blessings. It reigned over the Galar region in times of yore.
